     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** BBAN total length - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDBBANOK          1
     C                   PARM                    W#BBAN
